<div id="b">
<h2 class="secand-sec-bluebg expert padding-2">2.2 Set goals </h2>
<p>Goals and targets are important in life. It is the not the distance, the direction is important in life. Whatever we have done, it all depends on targets and goals. Time and resources are limited, we have to utilize the best. We have to set the targets and goals in personal, professional, organzatinal and social life. All are important for us. As we progress in our life these goals and targets keep changing. This is dynamic one and one need to review and change as per need of the hour. We have to keep the dynamic one. The SMART goals and targets to be set for us. </p>

<p><strong>2.2.1 - 4 Phases of life</strong> </p>
<p>There are 4 phases of life an 4 areas , we need to set the goals and targets for all phases and areas of life. We need to focus on overall success of life. There has to be balanced growth in life. Personal , professional , organizational and social , all are important for us. As we move from different phases of life from childhood to adult hood , we have to define the goals and targets of each stages. </p>

<p><strong>2.2.2 phases of life</strong>  </p>
<p><strong>2.2.3 set SMART goals and targets </strong> </p>
<p>Set you SMART  goals and targets. </p>
<p><strong>S- Specific</strong> – what we want to achieve – be specific  
<br><strong>M- Measurable</strong> – always set the target in measurable terms 
<br><strong>A – Achieve able</strong> – the target should be achieve able – it should be realistic in nature and able to achieve the same 
<br><strong>R – reasonable / realistic</strong> – make it more reasonable and realistic one , keep as close as it is possible to achieve. This would boost up your success 
<br><strong>T – time bound / time line</strong> – set it a time bound and timeline, never keep open ended 
<br>We need to follow all these mantra. </p>

<p><strong>2.2.4 manage your time </strong> </p>
<p>Just setting the goals and targets are not enough to give the result, what is important to mange you time. Need to understand what is normal, important and urgent. At given time number of work to be done, how to prioritize them . A decision making process is required, we may decide to leave or delegate some of the work which we may not like to do would not be adding higher value. A continuous efforts to be made for achieving the same. </p>

<p><strong>2.2.5 do the time management </strong> </p>
<p>Time management is very important. Number of time the Procrastination ( delay of work ) or not understanding the urgency of work , we have to pray huge price for the same. Taking the right decision at right time and with the right person is the wisdom. Wisdom is very important factor in our life. We need to develop the clear cut wisdom and goals in our life. </p>
